latestPosts.caption:
From a small village in Rajasthan to speaking on stage in Mumbai, Lalita’s journey is a powerful testament to what education can achieve.

Once struggling to write her own name, she now aspires to become a schoolteacher, demonstrating the profound impact of the right support and opportunities.

Behind every such transformation is @pgshiksha—the flagship CSR program of @proctergambleindia. For two decades, they have continued to enable children from underserved communities to soar.

When given a chance, children don’t just learn; they truly soar. 💫

With a commitment to education, P&G Shiksha continues to turn the dreams of over 50 lakh children into realities, transforming hope into opportunities for kids like Lalita to shine through education that lifts, not limits

 

#Ad #collab#WeAreYuvaa #PGShiksha #EraseTheLearningGap #20YearsofShiksha
